config BR2_KALRAY_TOOLCHAIN_DIR
	string "path to the Kalray toolchain"
	help
		Some packages build binaries and libraries with ClusterOS target.
		In general, they are based on Makefile.kalray.
		Makefile.kalray relies on KALRAY_TOOLCHAIN_DIR to find everything
		it needs in the toolchain. It does have have to be added in PATH.


